The types of technical data (you or your children) we might collect include:
• Timestamps of when you install or first open the app;
• Data on how you interact with the app;
• Your device ID;
•
• URLs you visited before or after using the app;
Information shared by advertising platforms like Unity, Inmobi, and Google Ads;
• Ads you view or click on; and
• General online behavior patterns.

When you or your children use our apps, we might collect certain personal information, including your email address, name, and age. This user/children's data is used for the following purposes:
• To verify your age;
• To save and track your game progress;
• To create and manage your user account;
• To enable gameplay across multiple devices;
•
To send promotional emails (if you have given consent); and
• To respond to any support inquiries you may send.

